data.description: Experience modern living in this newer-built home in the respected Rockford school district. Only minutes away from downtown Rockford, this move-in ready residence sits on a charming corner lot. Just a short stroll from the association clubhouse, pool, playground, and nature trail, it offers a lifestyle of leisure and recreation. The open concept living room, dining room, and kitchen create a welcoming space for hosting and gatherings. Convenience is key with a main-level laundry room and mudroom. Upstairs, three spacious bedrooms and two full baths provide comfort and privacy. The lower level extends the living space with an additional family room, bedroom, and full bath. Step outside onto the expansive back deck, perfect for both indoor and outdoor entertaining. With meticulous landscaping enhancing its curb appeal, this home is a dream inside and out.
